title: Sobo Katamuki Prefectural Natural Park (Miyazaki)
text: is a <a href="Prefectural%20Natural%20Park">Prefectural Natural Park</a> in northern <a href="Miyazaki%20Prefecture">Miyazaki Prefecture</a>, <a href="Japan">Japan</a>. Established in 1958, the park spans the <a href="Municipalities%20of%20Japan">municipalities</a> of <a href="Hinokage%2C%20Miyazaki">Hinokage</a>, <a href="Nobeoka%2C%20Miyazaki">Nobeoka</a>, and <a href="Takachiho%2C%20Miyazaki">Takachiho</a>. The park encompasses the Gokasho plateau, stretches of the Hinokage and Mōnose rivers, and .
